room_title: Escape room "Escape the Office" by Escape Challenge St. Louis in St. Louis
room_description: You work for a Scranton paper company. The overbearing, know-it-all Assistant to the Regional Manager is trying to stage a coup to take over as the Regional Manager. This would make life at the office even more unbearable if it were to happen.  See if you can escape from the office in time to stop him from meeting with the VP!
